298
00:18:36,590 --> 00:18:37,290
Don't waste money.

299
00:18:37,290 --> 00:18:38,420
Save up when you can.

300
00:18:52,240 --> 00:18:53,170
That's correct.

301
00:18:54,290 --> 00:18:54,820
And then?

302
00:18:58,400 --> 00:19:00,020
Then I used my phone at home

303
00:19:00,160 --> 00:19:00,720
