304
00:19:00,720 --> 00:19:02,380
from Wangzuo Malaban.

305
00:19:02,590 --> 00:19:03,920
It was delivered at 11:30 P.M.

306
00:19:03,920 --> 00:19:05,520
I went to sleep after eating.

307
00:19:07,000 --> 00:19:07,730
Verify this.

308
00:19:08,030 --> 00:19:08,560
Yes, sir.

309
00:19:12,880 --> 00:19:13,540
Don't rush.

310
00:19:15,200 --> 00:19:16,260
Make sure to figure

311
00:19:17,550 --> 00:19:18,400
everything out.

312
00:19:18,400 --> 00:19:18,930
Yes, sir.

313
00:19:25,090 --> 00:19:28,030
[Loyalty]

314
00:19:36,550 --> 00:19:38,150
Why would my name be written?

315
00:19:39,750 --> 00:19:41,510
Even if Ye had an issue with me,

316
00:19:42,200 --> 00:19:43,510
