317
00:19:43,510 --> 00:19:44,680
at a time like this.

318
00:19:45,550 --> 00:19:47,210
It indeed doesn't make sense.

319
00:19:49,240 --> 00:19:51,100
You just arrived in Sanjiangkou.

320
00:19:51,110 --> 00:19:52,640
Speaking of internal conflicts,

321
00:19:52,640 --> 00:19:54,170
you're the one benefiting,

322
00:19:54,790 --> 00:19:56,720
so you have no motive for the crime.

323
00:19:59,000 --> 00:20:00,730
If you were the one lying there,

324
00:20:00,920 --> 00:20:02,520
and wrote Captain Ye's name,

325
00:20:02,880 --> 00:20:05,010
that would actually be quite logical.

326
00:20:10,000 --> 00:20:10,360
I...

327
00:20:10,400 --> 00:20:12,350
I'm just speculating, hypothetically.

328
00:20:12,350 --> 00:20:12,880
No offense.

329
00:20:12,880 --> 00:20:14,070
None taken.

330
00:20:14,990 --> 00:20:15,720
I kind of wish

331
00:20:15,720 --> 00:20:17,070
I was the one lying there,

332
00:20:17,070 --> 00:20:17,830
and you all were here speculating

333
00:20:17,830 --> 00:20:19,290
about what happened to me.

334
00:20:20,830 --> 00:20:21,390
Chief!

335
00:20:22,830 --> 00:20:23,480
What is it?

336
00:20:23,720 --> 00:20:24,200
The person who delivered

337
00:20:24,200 --> 00:20:26,200
your food yesterday has been found.

338
00:20:26,640 --> 00:20:27,160
Found?

339
00:20:27,240 --> 00:20:27,860
Yes.

340
00:20:28,000 --> 00:20:29,160
You really found them?

341
00:20:29,160 --> 00:20:29,750
Are you sure?

342
00:20:29,750 --> 00:20:30,160
Yes.

343
00:20:35,110 --> 00:20:35,940
Thank you, Song.

344
00:20:35,940 --> 00:20:36,850
It's my job.

345
00:20:37,400 --> 00:20:37,790
I...

346
00:20:38,480 --> 00:20:39,070
Thank you.

347
00:20:39,030 --> 00:20:40,460
[Police]

348
00:20:39,200 --> 00:20:39,880
Good.

349
00:20:40,510 --> 00:20:41,590
Good. I'm glad it's found.

350
00:20:41,030 --> 00:20:46,990
[Police]

351
00:20:45,070 --> 00:20:45,870
I'm fine here.

352
00:20:45,960 --> 00:20:47,220
You can go back to work.

353
00:20:47,400 --> 00:20:48,540
I'll contact that person now

354
00:20:48,540 --> 00:20:50,670
to come to the station for a statement.

355
00:20:51,200 --> 00:20:51,800
Thank you.

356
00:20:54,880 --> 00:20:55,570
Chief.

357
00:20:55,880 --> 00:20:57,960
We found the witness
who delivered your meal.

358
00:20:57,960 --> 00:21:00,220
You're cleared of suspicion now, right?

359
00:21:01,920 --> 00:21:03,180
Will we still look into

360
00:21:03,270 --> 00:21:04,330
Captain Ye's case?

361
00:21:14,000 --> 00:21:15,820
Though I am in the clutch

362
00:21:16,160 --> 00:21:17,160
