363
00:21:18,000 --> 00:21:19,890
I thank whatever gods may be

364
00:21:20,510 --> 00:21:22,040
for my unconquerable soul.

365
00:21:24,030 --> 00:21:24,830
I understand.

366
00:21:25,000 --> 00:21:25,890
You mean

367
00:21:26,550 --> 00:21:28,480
you want to investigate to the end.

368
00:21:32,640 --> 00:21:33,560
How did you

369
00:21:33,590 --> 00:21:34,590
