370
00:21:35,270 --> 00:21:36,240
Weren't you just reciting

371
00:21:36,240 --> 00:21:38,070
William Ernest Henley's poem?

372
00:21:39,070 --> 00:21:41,310
I remember the next lines are:

373
00:21:42,070 --> 00:21:44,640
Under the bludgeonings of chance,

374
00:21:45,920 --> 00:21:47,920
