375
00:21:49,310 --> 00:21:50,440
My body is battered,

376
00:21:51,510 --> 00:21:52,640
my soul is bruised,

377
00:21:53,880 --> 00:21:55,030
but I am unafraid.

378
00:21:59,510 --> 00:22:00,640
Those are the lines.

379
00:22:01,680 --> 00:22:03,210
Chief, let's analyze this.

380
00:22:03,880 --> 00:22:05,510
Captain Ye

381
00:22:06,160 --> 00:22:08,590
didn't have this accident
at any other time.

382
00:22:08,590 --> 00:22:09,550
He was murdered

383
00:22:09,550 --> 00:22:11,390
right when you took office.

384
00:22:12,480 --> 00:22:14,970
And you clearly came down here

385
00:22:15,160 --> 00:22:16,790
