393
00:22:37,030 --> 00:22:37,510
Chief,

394
00:22:38,000 --> 00:22:38,960
we need to go through

395
00:22:38,960 --> 00:22:39,880
all the criminal cases handled

396
00:22:39,880 --> 00:22:40,920
in the year before Chief Lu died,

397
00:22:40,920 --> 00:22:41,690
