398
00:22:42,030 --> 00:22:43,350
to see if there are any clues.

399
00:22:43,350 --> 00:22:44,350
What do you think?

400
00:22:44,750 --> 00:22:45,440
I think...

401
00:22:46,510 --> 00:22:47,480
we can.

402
00:22:47,480 --> 00:22:48,480
We can take a look.

403
00:22:49,480 --> 00:22:50,550
It's just that I have a lot

404
00:22:50,550 --> 00:22:51,160
