405
00:22:51,160 --> 00:22:53,160
Don't worry about it. I'll go check.

406
00:22:54,480 --> 00:22:56,010
Thank you for your efforts.

407
00:23:00,240 --> 00:23:01,300
At such a young age,

408
00:23:01,460 --> 00:23:03,120
