409
00:23:06,020 --> 00:23:09,070
[Reason for borrowing: case investigation]
[Name: Ye Jian]

410
00:23:16,170 --> 00:23:17,550
[Criminal Investigation File]

411
00:23:21,200 --> 00:23:22,060
All filled out?

412
00:23:24,750 --> 00:23:25,760
Captain Ye

413
00:23:25,790 --> 00:23:27,200
