414
00:23:27,200 --> 00:23:27,510
Yes.

415
00:23:28,880 --> 00:23:30,480
What kind of cases were they?

416
00:23:30,640 --> 00:23:31,720
Cases Chief Lu was involved in

417
00:23:31,720 --> 00:23:33,030
the year before he passed away.

418
00:23:33,030 --> 00:23:34,360
They're all right here.

419
00:23:35,160 --> 00:23:35,690
Thanks.

420
00:23:39,550 --> 00:23:40,300
Li Qian.

421
00:23:41,790 --> 00:23:42,890
I was looking for you.

422
00:23:42,890 --> 00:23:44,220
What's wrong, Chief Qi?

423
00:23:48,110 --> 00:23:48,680
Yi'ang,

424
00:23:48,960 --> 00:23:49,960
