425
00:24:00,750 --> 00:24:02,880
The trace inspection results are out.

426
00:24:02,920 --> 00:24:04,550
The small stone used for writing

427
00:24:04,550 --> 00:24:05,680
only had

428
00:24:05,750 --> 00:24:07,680
Ye's blood and fingerprints on it.

429
00:24:07,680 --> 00:24:08,310
Around the body,

430
00:24:08,310 --> 00:24:10,270
