434
00:24:15,480 --> 00:24:16,680
right before he died.

435
00:24:20,640 --> 00:24:21,970
There's another thing.

436
00:24:22,240 --> 00:24:23,420
Why did you

437
00:24:23,880 --> 00:24:25,550
order food from Wangzuo Malaban?

438
00:24:25,550 --> 00:24:26,280
That place is

439
00:24:26,350 --> 00:24:27,750
