441
00:24:30,160 --> 00:24:31,020
It tastes good.

442
00:24:31,590 --> 00:24:32,910
Well... what's wrong?

443
00:24:33,350 --> 00:24:34,080
Chief Zhang,

444
00:24:34,480 --> 00:24:36,270
