447
00:24:39,880 --> 00:24:40,640
Missing?

448
00:24:42,640 --> 00:24:43,920
After the police went to the restaurant

449
00:24:43,920 --> 00:24:45,250
and confirmed with her,

450
00:24:45,720 --> 00:24:46,720
I wanted her to come to the bureau

451
00:24:46,720 --> 00:24:48,400
so we could ask a few questions.

452
00:24:48,400 --> 00:24:49,800
But when I called her,

453
00:24:50,270 --> 00:24:52,130
