461
00:25:28,000 --> 00:25:28,590
or even

462
00:25:29,200 --> 00:25:30,310
be unwilling to cooperate with my work.

463
00:25:30,310 --> 00:25:31,570
I can understand that.

464
00:25:31,830 --> 00:25:32,590
But everything

465
00:25:32,590 --> 00:25:34,120
has its limits, doesn't it?

466
00:25:34,200 --> 00:25:35,390
If someone is

467
00:25:35,790 --> 00:25:38,320
intentionally spreading rumors
to frame me,

468
00:25:39,680 --> 00:25:40,940
I cannot forgive that.

469
00:25:42,480 --> 00:25:44,280
What really makes us suspicious

470
00:25:45,270 --> 00:25:46,270
is her testimony.

471
00:25:55,260 --> 00:25:55,880
Li Qian.

472
00:26:07,070 --> 00:26:07,800
Chief Zhang,

473
00:26:08,640 --> 00:26:09,690
last night,

474
00:26:10,310 --> 00:26:11,310
I only dropped you off

475
00:26:11,310 --> 00:26:13,370
at the intersection near your house.

476
00:26:14,350 --> 00:26:16,480
Whether you actually went home or not,

477
00:26:17,120 --> 00:26:17,600
I...

478
00:26:19,400 --> 00:26:20,400
truly don't know.

479
00:26:43,740 --> 00:26:44,470
Chief Zhang.

480
00:26:45,550 --> 00:26:46,280
Chief Zhang.

481
00:26:48,720 --> 00:26:49,510
After that,

482
00:26:49,640 --> 00:26:50,920
you gave Ye a call,

483
00:26:50,960 --> 00:26:51,470
right?

484
00:26:52,310 --> 00:26:52,640
Yes,

485
00:26:52,720 --> 00:26:53,850
I did call him.

486
00:26:53,880 --> 00:26:55,120
Can I see your phone?

487
00:27:12,200 --> 00:27:13,160
At the time, why didn't you mention

488
00:27:13,010 --> 00:27:14,720
[Call Record] [Ye Jian]

489
00:27:13,640 --> 00:27:14,670
this detail?

490
00:27:21,240 --> 00:27:22,000
I forgot.

491
00:27:22,510 --> 00:27:23,710
I really just forgot.

492
00:27:24,160 --> 00:27:25,750
I made that call to Ye

493
00:27:27,270 --> 00:27:28,070
to have a talk with him.

494
00:27:28,070 --> 00:27:29,000
Talk about what?

495
00:27:30,550 --> 00:27:31,680
I just wanted to talk.

496
00:27:31,680 --> 00:27:32,700
Between us,

497
00:27:34,440 --> 00:27:35,990
there's no real conflict.

498
00:27:36,480 --> 00:27:37,030
We still have to

499
00:27:37,030 --> 00:27:38,350
work together in the future.

500
00:27:38,350 --> 00:27:39,790
I wanted to treat him to a meal.

501
00:27:39,790 --> 00:27:40,810
Treat him to a meal

502
00:27:40,960 --> 00:27:41,930
or have a talk?

503
00:27:47,400 --> 00:27:49,060
Chief Qi, what does this mean?

504
00:27:50,550 --> 00:27:52,400
Everyone just wants to understand

505
00:27:52,400 --> 00:27:54,000
the situation more clearly.

506
00:28:04,110 --> 00:28:04,640
Yi'ang,

507
00:28:04,830 --> 00:28:05,720
where are you going?

508
00:28:05,720 --> 00:28:06,400
I don't think you should

509
00:28:06,400 --> 00:28:07,590
