510
00:28:07,590 --> 00:28:09,650
I'll definitely stay out of the case.

511
00:28:10,070 --> 00:28:11,440
I need to find that delivery worker.

512
00:28:11,440 --> 00:28:12,640
Right now, only she can prove

513
00:28:12,640 --> 00:28:13,700
