514
00:28:15,550 --> 00:28:16,280
Is that okay?

515
00:28:18,350 --> 00:28:19,720
Don't just stand there.

516
00:28:19,790 --> 00:28:20,690
Go help look.

517
00:28:33,310 --> 00:28:35,620
[Police]

518
00:28:34,720 --> 00:28:35,250
Chief.

519
00:28:36,480 --> 00:28:36,960
Chief.

520
00:28:38,070 --> 00:28:38,730
Let me do it.

521
00:28:39,440 --> 00:28:40,000
Chief.

522
00:28:53,120 --> 00:28:53,740
Chief.

523
00:29:10,880 --> 00:29:11,490
Chief,

524
00:29:11,550 --> 00:29:12,810
