525
00:29:37,400 --> 00:29:39,050
Sorry, Song Xing.

526
00:29:39,440 --> 00:29:41,240
Chief, what's wrong?

527
00:29:42,480 --> 00:29:43,400
I shouldn't have said that

528
00:29:43,400 --> 00:29:44,800
