529
00:29:45,550 --> 00:29:47,150
You don't need to apologize.

530
00:29:47,200 --> 00:29:47,880
You don't need to apologize

531
00:29:47,880 --> 00:29:49,680
no matter how you scold or hit me.

532
00:29:49,830 --> 00:29:51,040
As police,

533
00:29:51,350 --> 00:29:51,880
we should

534
00:29:51,880 --> 00:29:53,480
doubt the doubt of the doubt.

535
00:29:54,240 --> 00:29:55,450
I said that myself.

536
00:29:56,110 --> 00:29:57,070
You are right

537
00:29:58,030 --> 00:29:58,830
to suspect me.

538
00:30:25,400 --> 00:30:25,900
Chief.

539
00:30:28,480 --> 00:30:30,060
Since I became a policeman,

540
00:30:31,590 --> 00:30:32,720
in every meeting,

541
00:30:33,200 --> 00:30:34,380
I have been thinking actively

542
00:30:34,380 --> 00:30:35,440
and eager to speak.

543
00:30:35,960 --> 00:30:38,270
I've made at least
hundreds of suggestions.

544
00:30:38,270 --> 00:30:39,350
But Captain Ye and the others

545
00:30:39,350 --> 00:30:40,810
have never accepted them.

546
00:30:42,790 --> 00:30:43,920
At the very beginning,

547
00:30:43,920 --> 00:30:45,250
they still let me speak.

548
00:30:45,750 --> 00:30:46,350
Now,

549
00:30:46,350 --> 00:30:48,350
they don't even let me talk in meetings.

550
00:30:48,350 --> 00:30:48,880
I have no idea

551
00:30:48,880 --> 00:30:50,410
