554
00:30:54,160 --> 00:30:55,590
About the joint DUI operation,

555
00:30:55,590 --> 00:30:56,310
I just went to you

556
00:30:56,310 --> 00:30:57,160
with the mindset of

557
00:30:57,160 --> 00:30:58,020
giving it a try.

558
00:30:58,400 --> 00:30:59,960
I didn't expect you to accept it

559
00:30:59,960 --> 00:31:01,560
without me even explaining.

560
00:31:02,920 --> 00:31:03,350
Later,

561
00:31:03,350 --> 00:31:04,920
when such a big thing happened,

562
00:31:04,920 --> 00:31:06,310
you still said I was right

563
00:31:06,310 --> 00:31:07,510
and that I helped you.

564
00:31:08,720 --> 00:31:09,980
What is appreciation?

565
00:31:10,350 --> 00:31:11,610
This is appreciation.

566
00:31:13,790 --> 00:31:14,380
Chief,

567
00:31:15,030 --> 00:31:16,360
when you said that,

568
00:31:16,480 --> 00:31:17,410
I made up my mind.

569
00:31:17,790 --> 00:31:19,990
I will follow you for the rest of my life.

570
00:31:29,990 --> 00:31:30,500
Xing,

571
00:31:31,440 --> 00:31:32,210
in my life,

572
00:31:32,630 --> 00:31:34,960
I have basically never misjudged anyone.

573
00:31:49,880 --> 00:31:51,060
Chief,

574
00:31:51,150 --> 00:31:52,420
