575
00:31:52,480 --> 00:31:54,280
of course I had to tell the truth.

576
00:31:54,920 --> 00:31:56,200
I did only drop you off

577
00:31:56,240 --> 00:31:57,900
at the intersection that day.

578
00:31:58,800 --> 00:31:59,930
But for this matter,

579
00:32:00,750 --> 00:32:01,830
you just need to prove that

580
00:32:01,830 --> 00:32:02,640
it was impossible

581
00:32:02,640 --> 00:32:04,240
