582
00:32:04,240 --> 00:32:05,310
Then it'll be over.

583
00:32:07,270 --> 00:32:08,870
You are a veteran detective.

584
00:32:09,440 --> 00:32:11,310
So smart and experienced.

585
00:32:12,310 --> 00:32:13,070
For you,

586
00:32:13,070 --> 00:32:15,030
