589
00:32:18,830 --> 00:32:19,700
Coming to Sanjiangkou,

590
00:32:19,700 --> 00:32:21,360
I should keep a lower profile.

591
00:32:21,830 --> 00:32:22,830
Now you are forcing me

592
00:32:22,830 --> 00:32:24,230
to rush to the front line.

593
00:32:24,880 --> 00:32:25,810
What should I do?

594
00:32:25,960 --> 00:32:27,270
Show off my skills to our comrades?

595
00:32:27,270 --> 00:32:28,590
-Just show us.
-Just show us.

596
00:32:28,590 --> 00:32:29,920
We really want to see it.

597
00:32:30,400 --> 00:32:31,550
Xing, stop driving in circles.

598
00:32:31,550 --> 00:32:32,750
I'm a little carsick.

599
00:32:34,200 --> 00:32:34,770
No,

600
00:32:35,070 --> 00:32:35,530
Chief.

601
00:32:35,560 --> 00:32:36,750
It's not that I'm driving in circles.

602
00:32:36,750 --> 00:32:37,310
You haven't told me

603
00:32:37,310 --> 00:32:38,370
where we are going.

604
00:32:39,480 --> 00:32:40,540
Where are we going?

605
00:32:40,590 --> 00:32:42,590
Wait a minute. I'm a little carsick.

606
00:32:42,590 --> 00:32:42,960
Okay.

607
00:32:49,220 --> 00:32:50,460
We found Jiang Ying's address.

608
00:32:50,460 --> 00:32:51,290
Follow me.

609
00:32:58,790 --> 00:32:59,270
Sir,

610
00:32:59,290 --> 00:33:00,750
what are you doing? Open the door.

611
00:33:00,750 --> 00:33:01,590
Going out?

612
00:33:01,750 --> 00:33:02,750
What do you think?

613
00:33:07,480 --> 00:33:08,210
This gate...

614
00:33:18,550 --> 00:33:23,020
[Yingzi General Store]

615
00:33:18,750 --> 00:33:19,640
Police!

616
00:33:19,790 --> 00:33:20,720
Is anyone there?

617
00:33:24,400 --> 00:33:25,600
How's the situation?

618
00:33:26,110 --> 00:33:26,510
Chief.

619
00:33:27,240 --> 00:33:29,300
I don't think there's anyone inside.

620
00:33:31,310 --> 00:33:32,310
Did you call them?

621
00:33:32,470 --> 00:33:34,330
Both their phones are turned off.

622
00:33:34,400 --> 00:33:36,260
Both their phones are turned off.

623
00:33:38,160 --> 00:33:38,830
Should we

624
00:33:38,830 --> 00:33:40,160
break the door open now?

625
00:33:41,680 --> 00:33:44,080
Chief Zhang is going to
break the door open.

626
00:33:49,550 --> 00:33:50,510
That's against protocol.

627
00:33:50,510 --> 00:33:51,480
They aren't criminals.

628
00:33:51,480 --> 00:33:52,640
We don't have a warrant.

629
00:33:52,640 --> 00:33:53,480
On what grounds can we break in?

630
00:33:53,480 --> 00:33:54,640
Who will take the blame
if something happens?

631
00:33:54,640 --> 00:33:55,310
Chief Qi said...

632
00:33:55,310 --> 00:33:56,770
I heard him. I heard it all.

633
00:34:01,000 --> 00:34:01,650
Look.

634
00:34:02,200 --> 00:34:03,160
When Captain Ye had his accident,

635
00:34:03,160 --> 00:34:04,270
this woman delivered food to me.

636
00:34:04,270 --> 00:34:04,670
Right?

637
00:34:04,720 --> 00:34:05,880
Now both of them have run away.

638
00:34:05,880 --> 00:34:06,790
Don't you find that suspicious?

639
00:34:06,790 --> 00:34:07,520
Suspicious.

640
00:34:07,830 --> 00:34:08,960
So do you agree to break in?

641
00:34:08,960 --> 00:34:09,800
I agree it's suspicious.

642
00:34:09,800 --> 00:34:10,920
But we need a warrant to force the door.

643
00:34:10,920 --> 00:34:11,840
With no warrant and no evidence,

644
00:34:11,840 --> 00:34:12,900
how can we break in?

645
00:34:13,480 --> 00:34:14,150
The evidence is inside.

646
00:34:14,150 --> 00:34:14,670
If I don't break in,

647
00:34:14,670 --> 00:34:15,400
how can I get the evidence?

648
00:34:15,400 --> 00:34:17,400
We can't break in without evidence.

649
00:34:20,370 --> 00:34:26,870
[Yingzi General Store]

650
00:34:41,880 --> 00:34:43,540
Chief Zhang has no solutions.

651
00:34:43,590 --> 00:34:44,510
He's helpless.

652
00:34:58,630 --> 00:34:59,330
I know

653
00:34:59,360 --> 00:35:00,320
I will be neglected

654
00:35:00,320 --> 00:35:01,850
in some corner of the world.

655
00:35:03,280 --> 00:35:03,960
The last remaining

656
00:35:03,960 --> 00:35:05,310
glimmer of light,

657
00:35:05,920 --> 00:35:07,260
at the end of life,

658
00:35:07,630 --> 00:35:08,680
will flicker

659
00:35:10,590 --> 00:35:11,790
and be extinguished.

660
00:35:13,070 --> 00:35:13,710
It's time

661
00:35:13,760 --> 00:35:15,890
for Chief Zhang's poetry recitation.

662
00:35:15,960 --> 00:35:16,820
Extinguished.

663
00:35:21,320 --> 00:35:22,050
Chief Zhang!

664
00:35:25,000 --> 00:35:25,730
Chief Zhang!

665
00:35:28,840 --> 00:35:30,040
This is the landlord.

666
00:35:31,360 --> 00:35:31,760
Hello.

667
00:35:31,760 --> 00:35:32,160
Hello.

668
00:35:32,550 --> 00:35:33,100
Ma'am,

669
00:35:33,670 --> 00:35:34,630
Jiang Ying, who lives here,

670
00:35:34,630 --> 00:35:35,590
is an important witness.

671
00:35:35,590 --> 00:35:36,480
Do you agree to let us

672
00:35:36,480 --> 00:35:38,630
to break the door open and investigate?

673
00:35:38,630 --> 00:35:39,410
No.

674
00:35:40,550 --> 00:35:42,010
Why do you need to break in?

675
00:35:44,030 --> 00:35:45,400
I have a key.

676
00:35:46,360 --> 00:35:47,360
Thank you, ma'am.

677
00:35:47,400 --> 00:35:48,670
Come on, turn on the body cams.

678
00:35:48,670 --> 00:35:49,110
Hurry up.

679
00:35:49,110 --> 00:35:49,710
Turn it on.

680
00:35:51,210 --> 00:35:54,780
[Police]

681
00:36:12,920 --> 00:36:14,030
Who is the person

682
00:36:14,070 --> 00:36:15,030
living with Jiang Ying?

683
00:36:15,030 --> 00:36:16,480
It's Jiang Ying's husband.

684
00:36:16,480 --> 00:36:17,880
I think his surname is Li.

685
00:36:18,000 --> 00:36:18,510
When they left,

686
00:36:18,510 --> 00:36:19,510
did they tell you?

687
00:36:19,710 --> 00:36:21,110
They didn't say anything.

688
00:36:21,110 --> 00:36:22,970
What could that couple have done?

689
00:36:23,440 --> 00:36:25,480
That man wouldn't even
dare to kill a chicken.

690
00:36:25,480 --> 00:36:26,670
The bedroom's in there?

691
00:36:26,670 --> 00:36:27,000
Yes.

692
00:36:47,030 --> 00:36:47,760
Chief Zhang.

693
00:36:50,000 --> 00:36:50,930
Hold this for me.

694
00:37:23,110 --> 00:37:24,440
The woman's height is between 1.60

695
00:37:24,440 --> 00:37:25,600
and 1.62 meters.

696
00:37:26,110 --> 00:37:27,590
She has a well-proportioned figure,

697
00:37:27,590 --> 00:37:29,450
weighs no more than 50 kilograms,

698
00:37:29,550 --> 00:37:30,680
and dresses neatly.

699
00:37:38,630 --> 00:37:39,500
She has fair skin

700
00:37:39,500 --> 00:37:40,720
and chestnut hair.

701
00:37:42,670 --> 00:37:43,760
Her footsteps?

702
00:37:43,780 --> 00:37:45,060
Light and fast.

703
00:37:48,340 --> 00:37:50,140
She speaks clearly and briskly.

704
00:37:50,440 --> 00:37:51,600
What about the man?

705
00:37:52,280 --> 00:37:53,210
I don't know about the man.

706
00:37:53,210 --> 00:37:54,940
How do you know about the woman?

707
00:37:55,070 --> 00:37:56,440
The woman delivered food to me.

708
00:37:56,440 --> 00:37:57,240
I've seen her.

709
00:37:59,070 --> 00:37:59,830
Here.

710
00:37:59,960 --> 00:38:01,150
Notify everyone immediately.

711
00:38:01,150 --> 00:38:02,550
Mobilize all police forces

712
00:38:02,550 --> 00:38:04,150
from surrounding towns
and police stations.

713
00:38:04,150 --> 00:38:06,070
Secure the bus and train stations,

714
00:38:06,070 --> 00:38:06,710
and all major entrances

715
00:38:06,710 --> 00:38:07,960
and exits of the city.

716
00:38:08,400 --> 00:38:09,670
Launch a citywide manhunt immediately.

717
00:38:09,670 --> 00:38:10,420
Tonight,

718
00:38:10,510 --> 00:38:11,190
we must catch them

719
00:38:11,190 --> 00:38:12,430
in Sanjiangkou.

720
00:38:12,490 --> 00:38:17,380
[Sanjiangkou Transportation Center]

721
00:38:30,550 --> 00:38:36,190
[Please keep one meter away]

722
00:38:56,250 --> 00:38:56,710
[Please keep one meter away]

723
00:38:57,050 --> 00:38:57,590
Let's go.

724
00:38:57,230 --> 00:39:01,550
[Please keep one meter away]

725
00:38:58,320 --> 00:39:00,320
A guy over there keeps looking at me.

726
00:39:00,510 --> 00:39:01,510
Could he be a cop?
